<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- rby yswʿ ạ̉nt ạ̹lh ʿṭwf wḍʿt ly ạlậyạt fy kl ṭryq ḥyạty
 qlt ạ̉nạ mʿkm kl ạlạ̉yạm wạ̹ly̱ ạnqḍạʾ ạldhr ln ạ̉trkkm
 ạlqrạr- mạdẖạ ạ̉ṭlb lḥnạnk ạ̉sẖtạq ạ̉sẖtạq lklmạtk ʿndmạ tnạdyny
 wtqwl yạ ḥbyby ạsmk mnqwsẖ ʿly̱ kfy wsẖʿrk mḥṣy̱ ldy
 2- fy ḍyqy ạ̉rạk tqwl yạ ḥbyby lạ tkẖf lạ̉ny ạ̉nạ mʿk
 tʿzyny fy ḥzny wtqwl yạ ḥbyby sạ̉msḥ kl dmʿk
 3- fy ṣlạty ạ̉nt wạqf tqwl yạ ḥbyby mạ tṭlbh bạlṣlạẗ tnạlh bạlạ̹ymạn
 tnạdyny fy tʿby wtqwl yạ ḥbyby tʿạla ly wạ̉nạ ạ̉ryḥk</lyrics>
<title>rby yswʿ</title>
